sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Browser
    participant NextAuth as NextAuth.js
    participant Google as Google OAuth
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    User->>Browser: Click "Sign In"
    Browser->>NextAuth: GET /signin
    NextAuth->>Google: Redirect to Google OAuth consent screen
    Google-->>User: Show consent screen
    User->>Google: Grant permission
    Google-->>NextAuth: Return auth code + profile
    NextAuth->>DB: Create/update User and Account records (Prisma adapter)
    DB-->>NextAuth: User object
    alt New User (no phone number)
        NextAuth-->>Browser: Redirect to /registration
    else Existing User
        NextAuth-->>Browser: Redirect to /dashboard
    end
